It is sometimes useful to think of this definition in terms of function composition: the net formula_424 is equal to the composition of the net formula_425 with the projection formula_426 that is, formula_427

For any given point formula_428 the net formula_421 converges to formula_430 in the product space formula_417 if and only if for every index formula_419 formula_433 converges to formula_434 in formula_435 
